---
import { Image } from "astro:assets"
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro"

---

<Layout>
    <div class="flex space-x-8">
        <div class="flex flex-col space-y-4">

            <h2 class="text-3xl">About IOK Engineering</h2>
            <p class="text-xl">our company profile in brief...</p>
    
            <p>Established in 1989, IOK Engineering has grown into one of most specialised bespoke solution manufacturers in the North West of England. The company is focussed on acheiving tailored fabrication of specialist tools and components - or simple reproduction tasks.</p>
                
            <p>Having moved to new premises, IOK Engineering continues to expand but also manages to keep customer satisfaction and individual relationships on a thoroughly personal level. Whatever you're particular need, the IOK team will aim to deliver an efficient and cost effective solution.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-col space-y-4 min-w-[100px]">
			<Image src="/cogs_small.jpg" alt="Airlock" width={100} height={100} />
			<Image src="/comms_sml.jpg" alt="Airlock" width={100} height={100} />
			<Image src="/bearings_small.jpg" alt="Airlock" width={100} height={100} />
		</div>
    </div>
</Layout>
